videos.description: Miami's Kendrick Norton goes down with an injury
videos.headline: Miami's Kendrick Norton goes down with an injury

videos.description: David Njoku picks up the first down with a hurdle over the Virginia Tech defender for a 12-yard gain and a play for the highlight reel.
videos.headline: Miami receiver goes up and over defender for first down

videos.description: Miami's Brad Kayaa goes deep but Virginia Tech breaks it up, batting the ball into the air where Terrell Edmunds makes the diving catch for the Hokies' interception.
videos.headline: Hokie makes spectacular diving interception

videos.description: Virginia Tech finds the end zone for the first time in the game when Jerod Evans finds Bucky Hodges from seven yards out to extend the Hokies' lead at 13-3.
videos.headline: Hodges makes the diving catch for a Hokies' TD

videos.description: Brad Kaaya pass complete to Ahmmon Richards for 39 yds to the VTech 36 for a 1ST down
videos.headline: B. Kaaya pass,to A. Richards for 39 yds for a 1ST down

videos.description: Needing a spark, Miami marches down the field and cashes in when Brad Kayaa hits Braxton Berrios for a 25-yard touchdown to cut the Hurricanes' deficit to 16-9 just before halftime.
videos.headline: Miami strikes back with TD just before halftime

videos.description: Jerod Evans pass complete to Bucky Hodges for 12 yds for a TD
videos.headline: Virginia Tech's Hodges fights in for second TD of the night

videos.description: Brad Kaaya hits a wide-open Chris Herndon for the 35-yard touchdown to answer a Virginia Tech score and cut the lead down to 23-16.
videos.headline: Miami's big-play TD cuts into Virginia Tech's lead

videos.description: Virginia Tech uses trickery at the goal line when running back Sam Rogers airs it out to Steven Peoples for the 13-yard touchdown, extending the Hokies' lead back to 14 at 30-16.
videos.headline: Hokies go to the bag of tricks with TD pass from FB

videos.description: Joey Slye 42 yd FG BLOCKED blocked by Jaquan Johnson
videos.headline: Miami blocks FG in the 4th

videos.description: Joseph Yearby run for 41 yds to the VTech 15 for a 1ST down
videos.headline: J. Yearby run for 41 yds for a 1ST down

videos.description: Jerod Evans run for 34 yds for a TD
videos.headline: J. Evans run for 34 yds for a TD

videos.description: The Virginia Tech defense records eight sacks in a 37-16 victory over Miami.
videos.headline: Virginia Tech makes easy work of Miami
